Vimium C Catppuccin Mocha

Catppuccin Mocha theme for the Vimium C browser extension.

Link Hint

Search

Usage

  1. Open Vimiums options page.
  2. Look for the Custom CSS for Vimium C UI option.
  3. Copy the contents of catppuccin-mocha.css into the textbox.
  4. Save the changes.
